<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Champaign1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Chámpaign</orth> or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Chámpain,</orth> subst., open country: <cit><quote>with shadowy forests and with --s riched,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.1.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 1, 65</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>daylight and c. discovers not more,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 2.5.173" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 5, 173</bibl></cit> (O. Edd. <emph>champian</emph>).
